def frequency_calculate(df,threshold):
    for i in df.columns:
        percentages=[]
        dict_of_counter=dict(Counter(X["{}".format(i)]))
        get_keys=list(dict_of_counter.keys())
        for j in get_keys:
            percentages.append(dict_of_counter[j]/X.shape[0])
        if pd.Series(percentages).gt(threshold).any()==True:
            features.append(i)

def get_low_correlated_columns(df,threshold,threshold2):
    for i in df.columns:
        if i=="Price":
            continue
        corr_value=np.abs(df.loc["{}".format(i),"Price"])
        if corr_value>=threshold:
            list_of_numerical_columns_to_keep.append(i)
        for j in df.columns:
            if i==j or j=="Price":
                continue
            corr_value1=np.abs(df.loc["{}".format(i),"{}".format(j)])
            if corr_value1>threshold2:
                dicts[i]=j
